<font color="yellow">Udaranya segar.</font>

764
01:10:39,741 --> 01:10:41,041
<font color="yellow">Kenapa kau tidak mau melihatku?</font>

765
01:10:45,411 --> 01:10:47,011
<font color="yellow">Kau merasa menyesal...</font>

766
01:10:47,511 --> 01:10:50,111
<font color="yellow">...kemarin itu mengumpat padaku?</font>

767
01:10:57,141 --> 01:10:58,241
<font color="yellow">Kenapa kau...</font>

768
01:11:00,111 --> 01:11:02,611
<font color="yellow">...ke gereja setiap hari...</font>

769
01:11:03,611 --> 01:11:04,911
<font color="yellow">...tengah-tengah malam?</font>

770
01:11:06,881 --> 01:11:08,111
<font color="yellow">Kau berdoa apa?</font>

771
01:11:10,211 --> 01:11:12,781
<font color="yellow">Aku berdoa kepada Tuhan dan
Bunda Maria...</font>

772
01:11:14,851 --> 01:11:16,541
<font color="yellow">...supaya mengampuniku.</font>

773
01:11:19,041 --> 01:11:21,981
<font color="yellow">Aku tidak merawat bayiku.</font>

774
01:11:25,581 --> 01:11:27,581
<font color="yellow">Aku dulu masih terlalu muda
dan tak tahu caranya.</font>

775
01:11:29,241 --> 01:11:30,641
<font color="yellow">Jadi aku minta pengampunan dosa.</font>

776
01:11:40,041 --> 01:11:42,681
<font color="yellow">Kenapa kau tak berdoa supaya mengampuniku
karena aku tak membantumu saat itu?</font>

777
01:11:43,741 --> 01:11:44,741
<font color="yellow">Aku juga sudah berdoa seperti itu.</font>

778
01:11:46,711 --> 01:11:49,241
<font color="yellow">Aku berdoa, kalau
hidupmu berat.</font>

779
01:11:50,581 --> 01:11:51,811
<font color="yellow">Aku meminta mereka untuk
mengampunimu.</font>

780
01:11:54,881 --> 01:11:56,081
<font color="yellow">Aku saat itu...</font>

781
01:11:58,011 --> 01:12:00,011
<font color="yellow">...juga sedang keguguran.</font>

782
01:12:04,081 --> 01:12:05,311
<font color="yellow">Aku pun sekarang masih menyesal.</font>

783
01:12:06,781 --> 01:12:07,851
<font color="yellow">Aku minta maaf.</font>

784
01:12:22,541 --> 01:12:24,611
<font color="yellow">Dunia harusnya yang...</font>

785
01:12:25,641 --> 01:12:27,511
<font color="yellow">...minta maaf pada kita.</font>

786
01:12:32,041 --> 01:12:33,741
<font color="yellow">Sudah dengar kabar bayi Ha Neul?</font>

787
01:12:36,781 --> 01:12:38,911
<font color="yellow">Aku senang. Sangat senang.</font>

788
01:12:43,781 --> 01:12:44,781
<font color="yellow">Tapi...</font>

789
01:12:46,011 --> 01:12:48,741
<font color="yellow">...suruh Min Ho pulanglah
ke rumahnya sekarang.</font>

790
01:12:51,711 --> 01:12:54,111
<font color="yellow">Aku tidak ingin membebani mereka.</font>

791
01:12:54,811 --> 01:12:56,741
<font color="yellow">Aku bisa hidup sendiri.</font>

792
01:12:57,941 --> 01:13:00,511
<font color="yellow">Aku bisa melakukan semuanya sendiri.</font>

793
01:13:01,851 --> 01:13:04,181
<font color="yellow">Jadi kau harus memberitahu mereka...</font>

794
01:13:05,241 --> 01:13:07,381
<font color="yellow">Kau dulu bisa hidup sendiri...</font>

795
01:13:09,351 --> 01:13:11,681
<font color="yellow">...dan bisa melakukan semuanya sendirian.</font>

796
01:13:14,351 --> 01:13:16,281
<font color="yellow">Tapi tidak lagi.</font>

797
01:14:22,742 --> 01:14:24,002
<font color="yellow"><i>[Bisakah Kita Bicara Yang Lain?]</i></font>

798
01:14:28,602 --> 01:14:29,802
<font color="yellow">Bukunya seru ya?</font>

799
01:14:30,672 --> 01:14:32,272
<font color="yellow">Dengarkan ini.</font>

800
01:14:33,402 --> 01:14:36,632
<font color="yellow">"Cara mempersiapkan hari tua."</font>

801
01:14:38,032 --> 01:14:40,402
<font color="yellow">"Saat kau kehabisan uang".</font>

802
01:14:40,772 --> 01:14:44,072
<font color="yellow">"Satu. Mencuri uang anak-anakmu."</font>

803
01:14:44,632 --> 01:14:47,602
<font color="yellow">"Dua. Beli lotere."</font>

804
01:14:48,242 --> 01:14:52,132
<font color="yellow">"Tiga. Coba mati-matian untuk
mendapatkan..."</font>

805
01:14:52,242 --> 01:14:54,132
<font color="yellow">"...uang pensiun dari negaram."</font>

806
01:14:55,532 --> 01:14:58,002
<font color="yellow">"Empat. Mulailah merokok."</font>

807
01:14:58,372 --> 01:15:00,672
<font color="yellow">Oh iya. Kau sudah berhenti merokok?</font>

808
01:15:01,332 --> 01:15:02,772
<font color="yellow">Apa ada cara nomor lima?</font>

809
01:15:03,602 --> 01:15:04,702
<font color="yellow">Sebaiknya kau berhentti merokok.</font>

810
01:15:06,932 --> 01:15:09,902
<font color="yellow">"Lima. Minum racun."</font>

811
01:15:11,002 --> 01:15:12,372
<font color="yellow">Buku yang sangat aneh.</font>

812
01:15:13,202 --> 01:15:14,702
<font color="yellow">Apanya yang aneh?
Ini sangat lucu.</font>

813
01:15:14,702 --> 01:15:16,102
<font color="yellow">Membuatku tertawa.</font>

814
01:15:18,802 --> 01:15:20,132
<font color="yellow">Aiyoo.</font>

815
01:15:20,932 --> 01:15:23,002
<font color="yellow">Hei, ada lagi.</font>

816
01:15:24,502 --> 01:15:26,702
<font color="yellow">Ibu akan mengubahnya
jadi kata-kataku sendiri.</font>

817
01:15:26,932 --> 01:15:27,932
<font color="yellow">Oke.</font>

818
01:15:28,172 --> 01:15:31,872
<font color="yellow">"Aku tahu apa yang kau inginkan."</font>

819
01:15:32,902 --> 01:15:35,832
<font color="yellow">"Aku tahu apa keinginan nenek, kakek..."</font>

820
01:15:35,832 --> 01:15:39,102
<font color="yellow">...dan pamanmu."</font>

821
01:15:39,532 --> 01:15:40,532
<font color="yellow">Apa itu?</font>

822
01:15:40,602 --> 01:15:44,002
<font color="yellow">"Tapi terlebih dari itu,
aku sangat tahu..."</font>

823
01:15:44,002 --> 01:15:47,242
<font color="yellow">"...apa yang kuinginkan."</font>

824
01:15:52,472 --> 01:15:54,572
<font color="yellow">"Aku tahu persis..."</font>

825
01:15:55,072 --> 01:15:57,472
<font color="yellow">"...dimana aku..."</font>

826
01:15:58,432 --> 01:16:01,132
<font color="yellow">"...seharusnya berada."</font>

827
01:16:03,702 --> 01:16:04,702
<font color="yellow">Dimana itu?</font>

828
01:16:07,272 --> 01:16:08,272
<font color="yellow">Di sampingmu.</font>

829
01:16:12,902 --> 01:16:15,242
<font color="yellow">Wan. Kalau ada yang terjadi...</font>

830
01:16:15,372 --> 01:16:16,372
<font color="yellow">Ibu.</font>

831
01:16:17,802 --> 01:16:20,672
<font color="yellow">Kita tidur saja malam ini.</font>

832
01:16:21,602 --> 01:16:23,532
<font color="yellow">Jangan bicara lagi.</font>

833
01:16:25,272 --> 01:16:27,272
<font color="yellow">Simpan saja dalam hati apa yang ingin
Ibu katakan.</font>

834
01:16:27,602 --> 01:16:29,202
<font color="yellow">Kita akan bicara setelah...</font>

835
01:16:30,632 --> 01:16:31,632
<font color="yellow">...operasimu selesai.</font>

836
01:16:32,202 --> 01:16:33,272
<font color="yellow">Barulah...</font>

837
01:16:33,632 --> 01:16:34,832
<font color="yellow">Wan.</font>

838
01:16:36,532 --> 01:16:37,532
<font color="yellow">Ibu.</font>

839
01:16:41,072 --> 01:16:42,072
<font color="yellow">Simpan saja dalam hati.</font>

840
01:16:43,532 --> 01:16:45,602
<font color="yellow">Aku tahu Ibu gelisah...</font>

841
01:16:45,602 --> 01:16:47,402
<font color="yellow">...untuk mengatakannya.</font>

842
01:16:49,132 --> 01:16:52,672
<font color="yellow">Jadi kau bisa menceritakan semuanya...</font>

843
01:16:53,302 --> 01:16:54,372
<font color="yellow">...saat operasi selesai.</font>

844
01:16:54,532 --> 01:16:56,372
<font color="yellow">Aku akan mendengarkannya.</font>

845
01:16:58,572 --> 01:16:59,572
<font color="yellow">Jadi simpan saja...</font>

846
01:17:01,172 --> 01:17:02,372
<font color="yellow">...dalam hati untuk saat ini.</font>

847
01:17:08,672 --> 01:17:09,672
<font color="yellow">Biarlah kita...</font>

848
01:17:11,272 --> 01:17:13,302
<font color="yellow">...berbicara untuk waktu
selama mungkin...</font>

849
01:17:15,532 --> 01:17:17,972
<font color="yellow">...setelah operasimu
selesai, ya?</font>

850
01:17:19,742 --> 01:17:23,832
<font color="yellow">Jangan ceritakan semuanya sekarang
seolah-olah ini waktu terakhir kita.</font>

851
01:17:26,032 --> 01:17:27,032
<font color="yellow">Baiklah.</font>

852
01:17:27,532 --> 01:17:28,832
<font color="yellow">Tapi, Wan...</font>

853
01:17:29,432 --> 01:17:30,702
<font color="yellow">Kau mencekikku.</font>

854
01:17:34,902 --> 01:17:36,602
<font color="yellow">Ya sudah, kucekik lagi.</font>

855
01:17:36,602 --> 01:17:39,402
<font color="yellow">Tulangku sakit.</font>

856
01:17:39,402 --> 01:17:40,802
<font color="yellow">Sudah.</font>

857
01:18:04,932 --> 01:18:05,932
<font color="yellow">Ibu.</font>

858
01:18:06,802 --> 01:18:07,802
<font color="yellow">Fighting.</font>

859
01:18:44,242 --> 01:18:46,502
<font color="yellow"><i>[Ny. Jang: Sedang Dalam Operasi]</i></font>

860
01:18:51,602 --> 01:18:52,632
<font color="yellow">Wan.</font>

861
01:18:53,802 --> 01:18:55,032
<font color="yellow">Kau butuh istirahat.</font>

862
01:18:55,902 --> 01:18:58,532
<font color="yellow">Pasti capek duduk diam
selama lima jam tanpa henti.</font>

863
01:19:01,302 --> 01:19:04,472
<font color="yellow">Dokter bilang butuh enam jam.</font>

864
01:19:05,702 --> 01:19:08,402
<font color="yellow">Pasti bakal buruk kalau operasinya
lewat dari waktu perkiraan...,</font>

865
01:19:08,402 --> 01:19:10,172
<font color="yellow">...tapi selesai terlalu cepat
juga lebih buruk.</font>

866
01:19:10,632 --> 01:19:11,832
<font color="yellow">Istirahatlah.</font>

867
01:19:15,972 --> 01:19:17,802
<font color="yellow">Yeong Won, waktunya kau minum obat.</font>

868
01:19:18,702 --> 01:19:19,702
<font color="yellow">Iya.</font>

869
01:19:20,572 --> 01:19:21,932
<font color="yellow">Bibi akan kembali.</font>

870
